xt\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 24, the IOC also voted to award the 2030 Winter Games to the French Alps.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.00985688038255e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it wasn't that long ago that 2023 was supposed to be the year when the IOC would settle on a site for the 2030 Winter Games, based on bids fromSalt Lake City; Sapporo, Japan; and Vancouver, Canada.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.00985688038255e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sapporo\", \"score\": 0.9968178291129879, \"rank\": 0.0031923294156507606, \"text\": \"Sapporo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sapporo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sapporo\"}, {\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.4969564716477644, \"rank\": 0.7472208683089596, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_natio